name: SVGComponentTransferFunctionElement
description: The SVGComponentTransferFunctionElement interface defines a base interface used by the component transfer function interfaces.

members.name: SVGComponentTransferFunctionElement.type
members.description: An SVGAnimatedEnumeration corresponding to the type attribute of the given element. It takes one of the SVG_FECOMPONENTTRANSFER_TYPE_* constants defined on this interface.

members.name: SVGComponentTransferFunctionElement.tableValues
members.description: An SVGAnimatedNumberList corresponding to the tableValues attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGComponentTransferFunctionElement.slope
members.description: An SVGAnimatedNumber corresponding to the slope attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGComponentTransferFunctionElement.intercept
members.description: An SVGAnimatedNumber corresponding to the intercept attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGComponentTransferFunctionElement.amplitude
members.description: An SVGAnimatedNumber corresponding to the amplitude attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGComponentTransferFunctionElement.exponent
members.description: An SVGAnimatedNumber corresponding to the exponent attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGComponentTransferFunctionElement.offset
members.description: An SVGAnimatedNumber corresponding to the offset attribute of the given element.
